  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Leetahm atleek/rangij/tas irr rak-\
stihhs to Israēta Kehnizu Laiku-\
Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schts bija ta KUNGA\nWahrds/ ko wiꞥſch us Jeūsu\nbijrunnajs/fazzidams: Lihdszet-\ntortain Augumain tew Behrni\nfehdehs us Israēta Gohda-Krehf-\nla/un tas irr ta notizzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sallums Jabeja Dehls\ntappe par Kehnizu trihsdefmits\ndewitā Gaddā Usijus ta Keh-\nniza no Juha/ un waldija wre-\nnu Mehnefi eekſch Samarijas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo Menaēms tas Dehls\nGadi/ nahze us augtchu no Tir-\nzas/ un nahze us Samariju/\nun kawe Sallumu Jabeja Deh-\nlu eekſch Samarijas/ un mofawe\nto/ un tappe par Kehnizu win-\nna Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas weht no Sallu-\nma Leetahm atleek/ un winna\nDerriba/ ko wiꞥſch irr darrijs/\nrangi/ tas irr rakstihts to Isra-\netā Kehnizu Laiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad kawe Menaēms Tiw-\nsu/ un winu/ kas eekſch tahs bt-\nja/ ir winna Rohbeschasnō Tir-\nzas/ tapehz ka tee winnam ne bij\n(Wahrtis) atdarrijufchi/ un\nwiﬀas gruhtas Seeivas wiꞥſch\nfatuppaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihsdefmits dewitā\nGaddā Asarijus ta Kehniza no\nJuha/ tappe Menaēms tas\nDehls Gadi par Kehnizu pabr\nIsraēlu/(un waldija) defmits\nGaddus eekſch Samarijas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija/ kas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tam KUNGA M ne patifke/\nwinsch ne afstahjehs no Jerobea-\nma Neebata Dehla Grehkeem/\nkas Israēlu grehkoht darrija/\nkamehr wiꞥſch dshwoja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atnahze Wuhls tas\nKehnisch no Affirijas prect to\nSemmi/ un Menaēms dwe\nWuhlam tuhkſtoſchus Talentus\nSudraba/ ka winna Rohka ar\nwinsu buhtu/ ka tas fawa Wal-\nstibā warreja stiprinatees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Menaēms iſspeede to\nNaudu no Israēta/ un ifkatraut\nBaggatam bijtam Kehnizam no\nAffura par ifkatru Wihru peez-\ndefmits Sudraba Sihektus doht-\nTad greeſahs tas Kehnisch no\nAffirijas atpakāk/ un ne palik-\nke wairs tai Semmē.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas weht no Mena-\neima Leetahm atleek/ un wiﬀs/ ko\nwiꞥſch irr darrijs/ tas irr rak-\nstihts to Kehnizu no Israēta\nLaiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Menaēms aisiniage\nar farweein Tehweem/ un Peka-\njus winna Dehls tappe par Keh-\nnizu winna Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peektadeſmiti Gaddā A-\nsarijus ta Kehniza no Juha/\ntappe Pekajus Menaēma Dehls\nvar Kehnizu pabr Israēlu eekſch\nSamarijas/ un (waldija) divi\nGaddus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un darrija/ kas tam\nKUNGA M ne patifke/ winsch\nne afstahjehs no Jerobema Nee-\nbata Dehla Grehkeem/ kas Isra-\nelu grehkoht darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Uiv\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
